{"tid":429373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攀出走廊鐵欄　27歲女子將軍澳墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-10-08T23:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T13:37:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58299e8c5ac924a8bce9859589c37063637ed253","tid":429373,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171009/large/1507495171_e94a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F1507495171_e94a.jpg&h=c53c7e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳茵怡花園7座，凌晨零時許，一名女子懷疑從高處墮下，被發現倒卧在天井地上，昏迷不醒，救護員到場，女子身體多處骨拆，當場證實死亡，警員封鎖現場展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n女死者姓陳27歲，居於上址一單位，相信她攀過走廊圍欄墮樓，警方調查後，初步認為案件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"655a0f392bca913ec1b748c9713abee626d79565","tid":429373,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:47:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57307821&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57307821%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171009&d=pJlKXLkXiGzccCl%2Fn%2FAQ67IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a7c75630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57307821%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171009&h=47c647dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57307821&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171009</a>"},{"pid":"0634a799f83469b0ca49c415bad3e09dc9911710","tid":429373,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r